OL,3,C'We've forgotten about our humanity':
OL,4,CMeghan decries 'toxicity' of social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FWhen asked how she tackled the
OL,8,F"seemingly endless toxicity" aimed at
OL,9,Fher online, she said: "It is really
OL,10,Finteresting as I can reflect on it, I
OL,11,Fkeep my distance from it right now for
OL,12,Fmy own wellbeing, but the bulk of the
OL,13,Fbullying and abuse that I was
OL,14,Fexperiencing on social media and
OL,15,Fonline was when I was pregnant with
OL,16,FArchie and with Lili.
OL,18,F"You just think about that and really
OL,19,Fwrap your head around why people would
OL,20,Fbe so hateful ` it is not catty, it is
OL,21,Fcruel."
