OL,3,C'We've forgotten about our humanity':
OL,4,CMeghan decries 'toxicity' of social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FThe former Suits actress said she
OL,8,Ffound it "disturbing" that women were
OL,9,F"spewing" hatred at each other online,
OL,10,Fadding: "I cannot make sense of that."
OL,12,F"If you're reading something terrible
OL,13,Fabout a woman, why are you sharing it
OL,14,Fwith your friends?" she said.
OL,16,F"Why are you choosing to put it out in
OL,17,Fthe world, what if it was your friend,
OL,18,For your mum or your daughter, you
OL,19,Fwouldn't do it.
