OL,7,F"I think that is the piece that is so
OL,8,Flost right now (with) what is
OL,9,Fhappening in the digital space and in
OL,10,Fcertain sections of the media ` we
OL,11,Fhave forgotten about our humanity and
OL,12,Fthat has got to change."
OL,14,FMeghan said that when she was 11 she
OL,15,Fwrote to Procter & Gamble and got an
OL,16,Fadvert changed, from saying
OL,17,Fdishwashing liquid was for women, but
OL,18,Ffor people all over America.
