OL,3,C'We've forgotten about our humanity':
OL,4,CMeghan decries 'toxicity' of social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FShe said: "It's funny to look back at
OL,8,Fit now as it was before social media,
OL,9,Fwhere you had a reach that was so much
OL,10,Fgreater, it was just an 11-year-old
OL,11,Fwith a pen and paper, but goes to show
OL,12,Fif you know there is something wrong
OL,13,Fand you're using your voice to
OL,14,Fadvocate for what is right, that (can)
OL,15,Freally land and resonate with people.
OL,17,F"Your voice is not small, it just
OL,18,Fneeds to be heard."
