OL,8,Femphasised that "representation
OL,9,Fmatters".
OL,11,F"The key thing that I think needs to
OL,12,Fbe focused on in terms of equity is
OL,13,Fit's not a zero-sum game, just because
OL,14,Fsomeone else has the same advantage
OL,15,Fthat you do doesn't mean that you're
OL,16,Flosing anything, and actually create
OL,17,Fan environment that is so inclusive,
OL,18,Fwhere people feel as if they have a
OL,19,Fseat at the table ` as they should,"
OL,20,Fshe said.
